title: Jidenna "The Chief" Album Stream, Cover Art & Tracklist | HipHopDX
text:
0 
Jidenna is here with his debut album, The Chief . 
After the success of his “ Classic Man ” single, Jidenna shares 14 tracks. Janelle Monáe , St. Beauty and Nana Kwabena appear on “Safari” with other guest appearances coming from Roman GianArthur and Nana Kwabena. 
The rapper/singer also made headlines when he appeared on Insecure in the fall. 
Stream Jidenna’s The Chief album and see the cover art and tracklist below. A Bull’s Tale Chief Don’t Run (f. Roman GianArthur) Trampoline
